This is the privacy policy for the game Traffic Driver by Flakos Developers.
In this game we respect the data and personal information of users.
We collect only the nickname that users specify and the highest score of users.
This data is used for world ranking. This leaderboard uses SilentWolf services (silentwolf.com) for cloud storage.
Here is SilentWolf's privacy policy https://silentwolf.com/privacy
We do not collect any other type of information, data or location, etc.
No personal data is stored outside the user's device, at least by Flakos Developers.
The only information that is stored on users' devices is the number of coins and the player's high score.
This is used only to display this data within the game.
In our games, user privacy is very important.

If you find any security vulnerabilities that were inadvertently caused by me, or have any questions
Regarding how the app protects your privacy, please email me at besadaferreralvaro@gmail.com and
I will surely try to solve it/help you.
